INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (322,'024','âœ¨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 requires perseverance and patience. While difficulties may arise initially, your fortune gradually rises toward the latter half of the year, bearing good fruit. This is a transitional period where the old departs and the new arrives, representing a late-blooming fortune that achieves success even if delayed. Through steady effort and sincere work, your aspirations will be fulfilled and prosperity will eventually eliminate difficulties. However, unstable energy exists in the first half, so avoid making major decisions hastily and act prudently. Praying at sacred mountains and great rivers will help you avoid misfortune and bring peace to your household. Like a bright moon rising with many people rejoicing, if you wait for the right time and prepare calmly, good opportunities will surely come.

âœ¨ 2. ğŸ’° Wealth and Financial Fortune
First-half wealth fortune is somewhat frustrating. Rather than expecting large profits, focus on maintaining the status quo and stability. In March and April, it''s important to stay within your means and avoid excessive greed. Reckless investments or business expansions may result in losses, so refrain from them. From September in the second half, fortune gradually rises and opportunities for unexpected wealth from others may arise. Wealth fortune lies in the eastern direction, so consider work or investments related to eastern regions. In November and December, steady accumulated efforts bear fruit, bringing stable income. Focusing on practical and reliable matters rather than grandiose plans will yield good results.

âœ¨ 3. ğŸ† Career and Promotion Fortune
Patience is also needed in your work life this year. In the first half, tasks may not progress easily and frustrating situations may continue. However, if you don''t give up and silently focus on your work, the situation improves from the second half. In June and July, it''s important not to carelessly discuss your business plans with others and maintain confidentiality. You may suffer damage from competitors or jealous people, so act cautiously. From October, good fortune gradually returns with auspiciousness in every endeavor. Subsequently, everything progressively prospers, so approach matters calmly. If you desire promotion or recognition, the second half is more favorable, and steadiness will eventually be acknowledged.

âœ¨ 4. â¤ï¸ Love and Marriage Fortune
Caution is needed in love and marriage matters. In the first half, rather than hastily advancing relationships, take time to fully understand each other. In February, associating with the wrong person may bring harm, so thoroughly assess potential partners and choose carefully. In August, be careful with words and actions to avoid disputes or gossip. From September, the atmosphere improves as auspicious energy returns, so discussing serious meetings or marriage during this period can yield good results. Married couples should communicate frequently with spouses for household harmony, and praying together at sacred mountains brings peace to the home. This is a year when patience and understanding strengthen relationships.

âœ¨ 5. ğŸ¥ Health Fortune
Special attention to health management is required this year. In January and March, you may feel physically unstable with accumulated fatigue, so get sufficient rest. Forcing matters beyond your capacity can harm your health, so don''t overestimate your stamina. The more scattered your mind, the more attention you should pay to health, making stress management very important. In June, abstaining from alcohol is advisable. Taking drinking lightly may lead to unexpected accidents or health problems, so be especially careful. In July and August, unknown worries may accumulate in your mind, so finding mental stability through meditation or prayer helps. In the second half, conditions improve, so recover strength through consistent exercise and regular living.

âœ¨ 6. ğŸ‘¥ Relationship Fortune
A selective and cautious attitude is needed in relationships. In February, beware of undesirable people in advance, and it''s wise to distance yourself from untrustworthy individuals. In August and September, don''t take disputes lightly and avoiding gossip is the best policy. It''s better to avoid any quarrels and be careful not to get involved in unnecessary arguments. In November, heading west may bring losses and gossip, so don''t make hasty decisions but judge carefully. Conversely, connections in the eastern direction are auspicious, so exchanges or cooperation with people from eastern regions are favorable. In December, you must sincerely cultivate relationships, and efforts to harmonize with relatives and close associates will form good relationships. Treating people with genuine sincerity will gain you solid connections in the latter half.

âœ¨ 7. ğŸ“š Academic and Self-Development Fortune
In academics and self-development, a year of persistent effort is needed. In January, don''t lament studying and work steadily. Although results may not show initially, you can achieve good outcomes even if delayed. In the first half, learning progress may feel slow, but if you don''t give up and continueåŠªåŠ›, your skills improve from the second half. From October, everything gradually prospers, so challenging exams or certification acquisition during this period is favorable. In December, enhancing concentration and finding mental stability through prayers at sacred mountains increases academic achievement. Setting practical and gradual learning plans rather than grandiose goals will ensure success. With patience and steady dedication, you will achieve desired results even if delayed.','January is a month of firmness and solidity, yet your body lacks peace and anxiety follows. Though welcoming the new year, it''s a period when your mind isn''t at ease and worries come first. It''s important not to covet things beyond your station and do your best in your current position. Excessive plans or greed become poisonous, so refrain from them.

Don''t lament studying and work steadily. Though results aren''t visible now, you can gain good fortune even if delayed. Pay special attention to health management, avoiding excessive schedules or overwork. Sufficient rest and regular living are necessary.

Wealth fortune is frustrating, so refrain from large investments or expenditures and focus on savings. Caution is needed in relationships, being careful with rash promises or words. The northern direction is relatively stable, with lucky colors being black and gray. Spend the month calmly while preparing for the next.','February is a month when associating with the wrong person may bring harm. It''s wise to beware of undesirable people in advance and distance yourself from untrustworthy individuals. A selective and cautious attitude is needed in relationships during this period.

If not related to legal matters, gossip or disputes may arise, so be prepared. Be careful with words and actions, being cautious not to get involved in unnecessary arguments. However, it won''t cause major damage, so there''s no need for great concern.

Wealth fortune is ordinary, making it difficult to expect special income. Focus on maintaining the status quo and pursuing stability. At work, silently dedicate yourself to your tasks. Health is acceptable but stress management is necessary.

Wisdom is needed to review relationships with close people, strengthening good connections while organizing harmful ones. The eastern direction is relatively auspicious, with lucky colors being light green and beige. Spend the month carefully.','March is a month requiring caution against disputes and quarrels due to solid misfortune. The more scattered your mind, the more attention you should pay to health, with mental stability being most important. Since stress easily accumulates during this period, calm your mind through meditation or light exercise.

Even if your body is in difficulty, as long as your residence is secure, there''s no major problem, so ensure your living environment isn''t unstable. Maintaining a stable life foundation is the secret to getting through this period well.

Wealth fortune is poor. Even with steady work, gaining wealth is difficult, making this a month with little income. Vain plans or reckless business ventures bring losses, so refrain from them. Focus on current work and postpone new challenges.

At work, quietly dedicate yourself to your duties and avoid standing out. Pay special attention to health management, avoiding overwork and getting sufficient rest. Lucky colors are gray and brown, with staying stably at home being advisable.','April is a difficult month like rowing a boat against the current. With many obstacles preventing easy progress in everything, rather than forcing matters, wisdom to wait for the right time is needed. Proceeding forcefully may lead to even greater difficulties.

Making vain statements or plans will surely be disadvantageous, so focus only on realistic and certain matters. Dishonest plans eventually fail, making honest behavior important. Don''t pursue unreasonable undertakings.

Wealth fortune is very poor. Absolutely refrain from large expenditures or investments, spending only the minimum necessary. At work, be careful to avoid mistakes and prevent friction with superiors or colleagues.

Health also requires caution. Since overwork or stress may weaken your body, get sufficient rest and pay attention to nutritional intake. Avoid the northern direction, with lucky colors being white and light blue. Spend time quietly while preparing for next month.','May is a month as dark as a night path where even the candle has gone out. Since it''s easy to lose direction without distinguishing north, south, east, or west, postpone important decisions and focus on maintaining the status quo. Moving hastily may cause you to lose your way.

If you take alcohol lightly, strange events will approach right before your nose, making them difficult to avoid. Thoroughly abstain from drinking and stay away from entertainment or indulgence. A moderate attitude is needed for health and safety.

However, since gains lie in the east, you can surely obtain wealth. Focusing on work or exchanges with people related to the eastern direction can help you seize small opportunities. Boldly turn your attention eastward.

At work, quietly focus on your tasks and refrain from unnecessary words or actions. Caution is also needed in relationships, avoiding situations that might cause misunderstandings. Only the eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being green and bright blue. Absolutely stay away from alcohol and focus on health management.','June is a month when nothing you execute will be accomplished due to difficulties waiting ahead. Don''t seek gains from afar but find stability nearby. Ambitious plans are likely to all end in failure.

Discussing your business plans with others will bring great harm, so thoroughly maintain confidentiality. If information leaks to competitors or jealous people, plans may collapse or face obstruction. Be careful with your words and act cautiously.

Even if gossip doesn''t arise, legal problems or unfortunate misfortunes may occur. To avoid getting involved in legal issues, handle all matters transparently and carefully review contracts and documents.

Since both wealth and career fortune are poor during this period, postpone new challenges and focus on maintaining the current state. Health also requires attention, with stress management being important. Lucky colors are gray and black, with staying quiet being the best policy.','July is a month like a pie in the sky that you can''t believe even when seeing it. Since thoughts are infinite but implementation is impossible, don''t fall into vain plans or fantasies but face reality. This is a period when the gap between ideals and reality is large.

Since the sun and moon aren''t bright, there will be solidness in your body. Special attention to health management is needed, and illness may develop if you don''t take good care of your body. Sufficient rest and nutritional intake are necessary.

Since unknown worries will exist in your heart, who will understand this matter? It''s a frustrating and lonely period. Don''t worry alone but talk with someone you trust, or find peace of mind through meditation and prayer.

Wealth fortune is hard to expect, and frustrating situations continue in work life. Rather than attempting major changes, focus on maintaining the status quo and strive to find inner stability. In relationships, light exchanges are better than deep conversations. Lucky colors are white and pale yellow, with religious or meditation activities being helpful.','August is a month when disputes shouldn''t be taken lightly. Since avoiding gossip is difficult, avoiding any quarrels is the best policy. Be careful with words and actions, being cautious not to get involved in unnecessary arguments.

However, since auspicious spirits have returned, it''s finally like vegetation enjoying pleasure. Like spring energy returning, good energy gradually begins to circulate. You can feel that difficult times are slowly ending.

Others'' wealth coincidentally enters your home - how could this not be joyful? Since unexpected income or help may come, accept it with a positive mind. Small fortunes are finding you during this period.

At work, quietly focus on your tasks while making efforts to improve relationships with people around you. Health shows signs of recovery, so build strength through consistent exercise and regular living. Eastern and southern directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being light green and sky blue. If you''re just careful about disputes, this can be a good month.','September is a month when auspicious energy gradually begins to return. Don''t covet or try to manage other things beyond your means - staying within your station is important. Reckless expansion or new challenges will bring harm, so refrain from them.

Since good fortune has begun to gradually return, there will be auspiciousness in every hundred matters. From now on, situations improve and opportunities come, so prepare with a positive mind. Difficult times are ending.

Subsequently, everything will gradually prosper, so approach matters calmly. Rather than hastily rushing, taking steps gradually will yield good results. This is a period when you feel the rewards of patience.

Wealth fortune also gradually improves, and you begin receiving recognition at work. Health recovers, allowing you to regain vitality. Relationships also become harmonious, and new connections may arrive. Eastern and southeastern directions are auspicious, with lucky colors being green and gold. Stay within your means and calmly wait for opportunities.','October is a month when reckless behavior makes avoiding misfortune difficult. Insincere actions or hasty decisions invite disputes, so act carefully. Refrain from impulsive behavior and act after deep thought.

If you uphold what is right and pursue stability, you will almost avoid this misfortune, so stay within your means. Maintaining honest and sincere attitudes consistently allows you to avoid problems. Keeping to principles is the safest path.

If you head west, there will be losses and gossip. It''s better to avoid the western direction or matters related to western regions. Conversely, eastern or southern directions are relatively safe.

Don''t make hasty decisions but judge with sufficient time. Postponing important matters to next month is also a good method. Wealth fortune is ordinary, and at work, handle tasks stably. Health is acceptable but stress management is needed. The eastern direction is auspicious, with lucky colors being blue and white.','November is a month of mid-winter fortune with neither losses nor gains, where fortune and misfortune are mixed. Since it''s a period flowing ordinarily without major changes, focus on maintaining the status quo and pursuing stability.

Since wealth lies in the east, you can surely obtain it by going out. Taking business trips eastward or dealing with people from eastern regions can bring small profits. Actively utilize the east.

If you work steadily, you will see results. Since efforts made thus far are beginning to bear fruit little by little, don''t give up but continue working sincerely. Steadiness is the key to success.

Benefits will surely arise among relatives and close people, and you must sincerely cultivate relationships. Strengthening relationships with family and friends and cherishing people around you can bring help. This is a period when connections bring wealth and opportunities. The eastern direction is most auspicious, with lucky colors being green and brown.','December is a month that surely brings prosperity. Efforts and patience thus far bear fruit, achieving good results. This is a period when you can feel rewarded while wrapping up the year.

Missing this opportunity will bring irreversible regrets. Don''t miss the opportunities that come and actively utilize them. Now is the time to make important decisions.

Praying at sacred mountains and great rivers will bring peace to your household, so offer prayers sincerely. Religious activities or spiritual practices bring peace of mind and household harmony. Wrap up the year with a grateful heart.

Since unfortunate misfortune still remains, don''t move your body carelessly but protect yourself with a prayerful attitude. Finishing the year with a careful and humble attitude will bring greater blessings next year. Since wealth and career fortune improve, approach matters actively but don''t be excessively greedy. All directions are relatively auspicious, with lucky colors being gold and silver.','2025-03-02 03:02:01.080985+00','e');

